Interface AggregatedIntegerMetric

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, Metric, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
AggregatedIntegerMetricImpl
public interface AggregatedIntegerMetric
extends Metric

A representation of the model object 'Aggregated Integer Metric'.

The following features are supported:

  • Minimum
  • Maximum
  • Median
  • Average
  • Standard Deviation

See Also:
